1.title: All About the Sun

episode of.title: Wicca and Witchcraft for beginners (TV Series 2016– )

1.plot: In this course we will explore Witchcraft and Wicca. We will learn about the secret society's history, beliefs, tools, rituals, responsibilities and magic. Witches manipulate the infinite energy that surrounds us in order to promote their wishes and desires. We are going to explore this idea and try to tap into this mysterious energy with this ancient hidden wisdom and craft.
